OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRikki Neave: Mother of     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmurdered schoolboy says 'I 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdied when he did'          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The mother of a six-year-old schoolboy 
OL,6, murdered in 1994 said "when Rikki died,
OL,7, I died" as she prepares for her son's  
OL,8, killer to be sentenced.                
OL,10,FRikki Neave's naked body was found near
OL,11,Fhis Peterborough home the day after he 
OL,12,Fdisappeared in November 1994.          
OL,14,FIn April this year, James Watson, now  
OL,15,F41 but 13 at the time of Rikki's death,
OL,16,Fwas found guilty of his murder.        
OL,18,FRikki's mother Ruth Neave - who was    
OL,19,Fcleared of murder in 1996 - told a BBC 
OL,20,Fdocumentary she wants a police apology.
